packOptions.summary: IReadOnlySet implementaion with helpers to inject into current BCL.
packOptions.releaseNotes:
Implements missing IReadOnlySet contract, along with:
IReadableSet - full, but not contravariant version of IReadOnlySet
HashSetEx - extended HashSet with new contracts implementation
ReadOnlyExtensions + wrappers - that helps to inject IReadOnlySet on current BCL.
